'''2016年南亞運動會羽毛球比賽'''為[[2016年南亞運動會|第12屆南亞運動會]]的其中一項競賽項目，共產生七面金牌；賽事於2016年2月6日至2月10日在[[印度|印度]][[古瓦哈提|古瓦哈提]]舉行。

雖然東道主印度一些世界頂級好手（如[[塞娜·内维尔|塞娜·内维尔]]和[[卡夏普·帕鲁帕利|卡夏普·帕鲁帕利]]等）賽前因傷未能參賽，但整體實力仍遠高於其他隊伍<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Saina to lead full-strength badminton squad for 12th South Asian Games in February|url=http://www.firstpost.com/sports/saina-to-lead-full-strength-badminton-squad-for-12th-south-asian-games-in-february-2600620.html|agency=First Post|date=2016-01-27|accessdate=2016-07-04|archive-date=2016-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161110021702/http://www.firstpost.com/sports/saina-to-lead-full-strength-badminton-squad-for-12th-south-asian-games-in-february-2600620.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Saina Nehwal, Kashyap ruled out of South Asian Games|url=http://www.news18.com/news/badminton/injured-kashyap-ruled-out-of-south-asian-games-1199202.html|agency=Network18 Media|date=2016-02-04|accessdate=2016-07-04|archive-date=2016-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820002215/http://www.news18.com/news/badminton/injured-kashyap-ruled-out-of-south-asian-games-1199202.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。結果，印度選手囊括了全部賽事的七面金牌，以及壟斷了五個單項的決賽位置，並以七金五銀成為本項目的大贏家<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=South Asian Games : Ruthvika Shivani Upset PV Sindhu To Win Gold|url=http://xtratime.in/more-sports/south-asian-games-ruthvika-shivani-upset-pv-sindhu-to-win-gold/|agency=xtratime|date=2016-02-10|accessdate=2016-07-04|archive-date=2016-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160223012008/http://xtratime.in/more-sports/south-asian-games-ruthvika-shivani-upset-pv-sindhu-to-win-gold/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="team">{{en}}{{cite news|title=India’s Badminton Team Clinches Gold at South Asian Games|url=http://www.indiawest.com/sports/india-s-badminton-team-clinches-gold-at-south-asian-games/article_78f9747e-cead-11e5-a926-1bae1711eb74.html|agency=India West|date=2016-02-08|accessdate=2016-07-04|archive-date=2016-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160803233256/http://www.indiawest.com/sports/india-s-badminton-team-clinches-gold-at-south-asian-games/article_78f9747e-cead-11e5-a926-1bae1711eb74.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ws">{{en}}{{cite news|title=South Asian Games: Ruthvika Shivani stuns PV Sindhu|url=http://www.deccanchronicle.com/sports/badminton/110216/south-asian-games-shuttler-ruthvika-shivani-stuns-pv-sindhu.html|agency=India West|date=2016-02-11|accessdate=2016-07-04|archive-date=2016-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160505104207/http://deccanchronicle.com/sports/badminton/110216/south-asian-games-shuttler-ruthvika-shivani-stuns-pv-sindhu.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

